quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,Sε Ye’hu wͻn mmͻbͻ na Y’eyi ͻhaw a εwͻ wͻn soͻ no fri wͻn so mpo a wͻ’bεtͻ akͻ wͻn asoͻden no so wͻ anifira mu
  23,76,"Nokorε sε, Yε’de asotwee sͻͻ wͻn mu, nanso w’ammrε wͻn ho ase amma wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn, na wͻ’ango wͻn ho ansu anfrε no"
  23,77,"Kͻpem εberε a Ye’bebue apono a εkͻ asotwee kεseε no mu ama wͻn, εhͻ na wobehunu sε wᴐn apa aba"
  23,78,"Ɔno na W’abͻ aso, ne ani ne akoma ama mo. Ayeyie ketekete na mode ma (Nyankopͻn)"
  23,79,"Ɔno na Oduaa mo wᴐ asaase no soᴐ, na Nehᴐ na mobehyia"
  23,80,"Ɔno na Ɔma nkwa εna Okum, adesaeε ne adekyeε abirabͻ nso wͻ no. Adεn, monni nteaseε anaa"
  23,81,"Aaane, wͻ’ka deε tetefoͻ no kaeε no ara bi"
  23,82,"Wͻ’ka sε: “Enti εyε nokorε ampa sε yebenyane yεn aberε a yawuo ayε mfuturo ne nnompe"
  23,83,Ampa sε yεde woi hyεε yεn ne y’agyanom a wͻ’dii kan no bͻ. Nokorε sε woi yε tetefoͻ no anansesεm
  23,84,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Hwan na asaase ne wͻn a εwͻ soͻ no yε ne dea, sε monim ampa a"
  23,85,"Wͻ’bεka sε: ”Ɛwͻ Nyankopͻn“. Ka sε: “Ɛna monfa nyε afutuo?”"
  23,86,"Ka sε: “Hwan ne ͻsoro nson no ne Ahennwa Kεseε no Wura?”"
  23,87,"Wͻ’bεka sε: “Ɛwͻ Nyankopͻn “. Kasε: “Ɛna enti monnsuro?”"
  23,88,"Kasε: ”Hwan na biribiara ho tumi wͻ nensa mu na ͻbͻ (biribiara) ho ban, na (obiara) mmͻ Neho ban, sε monim ampa a"
  23,89,"Wͻ’bεka sε: “Ɛwͻ Nyankopͻn“. Ka sε: “Na afei adεn na moredaadaa moho?”"
  23,90,"Aane, Yεde Nokorε no abrε wͻn, na ampa sε wͻ’yε atorofo (wͻ nsεm a wͻ’ka fa Nyankopͻn ho no)"
  23,91,"Nyankopͻn nwoo ba biara, na awurade biara nso nka Ne ho; (sε εte saa a) anka awurade biara bεfa deε ͻbͻeε akͻ, na anka (awurade no) binom bεma wͻn ho so wͻ ebinom so. Kronkron Hene ne Nyanko-pͻn, Ɔyε Kεse kyεn deε wͻ’de susu no no"
  23,92,"Ahuntasεm ne badwam Nimdefoͻ no, Ɔkorͻn kyεn deε wͻ’de bata (Ne ho nyinaa)"
  23,93,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: ”Me Wura Nyankopͻn, sε Worema me ahunu (asotwee) a W’ahyε wͻn ho bͻ no a"
  23,94,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn, εneε εnfa me nka nnipa bͻnefoͻ no ho.“"
  23,95,"(Nkͻmhyεni), nokorε sε Yε’betumi nso akyerε wo (asotwee) a Y’ahyε wͻn ho bͻ no"
  23,96,Fa adeε a εyε papa si bͻne ho kwan. Ye’nim nsεm a wͻ’keka no nyinaa
  23,97,"Ka sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, mehwehwε Wo hͻ ntwitwagyeε afri ͻbonsam adwen bͻne a ͻwesa hyε nnipa mu no ho"
  23,98,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn, mesan nso hwehwε Wohͻ ntwitwagyeε sε anhwε a na wͻn aba me ho"
  23,99,"(Abͻneεfoͻ yi de no saa ara) kͻpem sε, owuo bεba wͻn mu bi soͻ, (εhͻ na) ͻbεka sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, mamensan nkͻ (wiase bio)"
  23,100,"Sεdeε (mεkͻ) akᴐyԑ adwuma pa a m’anyε no“. Daabi, εno deε εyε asεm bi kwa na ͻkaeε. Ɛban si wͻn akyi kͻpem εda a wͻ’bεsͻreε (afri owuo mu)"
  23,101,"Enti sε yεbͻ Totorobεnto no mu a, saa Da no abusua bͻ biara nna wͻn ntεm, na obi mmisa obi (asεm)"
  23,102,Wͻn a wͻn nsania mu bεyε duro (wͻ papayԑ mu) no wͻn ne nkonimdifoͻ no
  23,103,"Na wͻn a wͻn nsania mu bεyε hare (wͻ papayε mu) no, saa nkorͻfoͻ no na wͻn ayera wͻn kraa, Amane hunu gya no mu na wͻ’bεtena"
  23,104,"Egya no bεhye wͻn anim, ayi (wͻn) anofafa (afri hͻ) awene wͻn se wͻ (Ogya no) mu"
  23,105,"(Yebebisa wͻn sε): Enti yankenkan Mensεm no ankyerε mo εna mobuu no atorͻsεm"
  23,106,"Wͻ’bεka sε: ”Ye’Wura Nyankopͻn, ya’hokyere anaa ohia broo yεn so, εna yεbεyεε nnipa a wͻn ayera"
  23,107,"Ye’ Wura Nyankopͻn, (yεsrε Wo sε): Yi yεn fri (Amanehunu gya yi ) mu, na sε yε’san kͻ (yε bͻne) bio a, nokorε sε na yε’yε abͻneεfoͻ ampa"
  23,108,"Nyankopͻn bεka sε: ”Monfri hͻ nkͻ (Ogya no) mu, na monnkasa Me ho “"
  23,109,"Nokorε sε na Menkoa no mu bi ka sε: “Ye’Wura Y’agye adi, enti fa (yε’bͻne) kyε yεn na hu yεn mmͻbͻ na ampa sε, Wone ahummͻborͻfoͻ no mu Mmͻborͻhunu Hene no"
  23,110,Nanso modii wͻn ho fεw kͻpem sε mowerε frii Meho nkaekaeε na moseree wͻn
  23,111,"Wͻn aboterε a wͻ’nyaeε no ho nti, M’atua wͻn so ka nnε, nokorε sε wͻne nkonimdifoͻ no”"
  23,112,"(Nyankopͻn) bεka sε: ”Mfi dodoͻ sεn na mode tenaa asaase no soͻ?”"
  23,113,"Wͻ’bεka sε: ”Yε’tenaa dakoro anaasε dakoro mu fa bi”. Ɛneε bisa wͻn a wͻ’bu (εberε no ho) akonta no"
  23,114,"(Nyankopͻn) bεka sε: “Ɛberε tiaa bi na mode tenaa (wiaseε) nokorε sε na anka monim a”"
  23,115,Enti modwen sε Yε’bͻͻ mo kwa a enti monnsan mma Yεn hͻ (mmebu akonta)
  23,116,"Okokuroko ne Nyankopͻn, Ɔhene Nokwafoͻ no, Nyankopͻn biara nni hͻ gyesε Ɔno nko ara, Ɔno ne Animuonyam Ahennwa Wura no"
  23,117,"Obi a obesu afrε nyame foforͻ bi aka Nyankopͻn ho, abrԑ a onni nyinasoͻ bi saa no, n’akontabuo deԑ ԑwͻ ne Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ. Nokorε sε boniayεfoͻ no deε wͻ’nni nkonim"
  23,118,"(Nkͻmhyεni), kasε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, fakyε (yεn) na hu (yεn) mmͻbͻ, na Wone Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ no mu Mmͻborͻhunu Hene papa no"